OL,3,CMan admits encouraging or assisting
OL,4,Csuicide by selling chemicals online
OL,6,FA man from north Wales accused of four
OL,7,Fcounts of encouraging or assisting
OL,8,Fsuicide by selling chemicals online
OL,9,Fhas pleaded guilty at Mold Crown Court
OL,10,Ftoday.
OL,12,FMiles Cross, 33, of Llys Nantgarw in
OL,13,FWrexham, set up a business selling the
OL,14,Fchemical via an internet discussion
OL,15,Fforum and interacted under a pseudonym.
OL,17,FHe has been released on bail, and is
OL,18,Fexpected to be sentenced at Mold Crown
OL,19,FCourt on 7 January 2026.
