OL,6,FJudge Rhys Rowlands said "this is an
OL,7,Funusual case but it's a worrying case".
OL,9,FCross joined the site in July 2024 and
OL,10,Fposted a QR code, which allowed people
OL,11,Fto order the chemical directly from
OL,12,Fhim and pay via his bank account.
OL,14,FCross received payments of #100 from
OL,15,Ffour people and sent them the chemical
OL,16,Fthrough the post. The court heard two
OL,17,Fpeople took their own lives as a
OL,18,Fresult.
