OL,6,FWhen police searched Cross's address
OL,7,Fin January 2025, officers discovered
OL,8,Famounts of the chemical and other
OL,9,Fparaphernalia.
OL,11,FPolice analysis of Cross's seized
OL,12,Fdevices also linked him to the forum,
OL,13,Fsocial media profiles, and the bank
OL,14,Faccount.
OL,16,FToday at Mold Crown Court, Cross
OL,17,Fpleaded guilty to four offences of
OL,18,Fencouraging or assisting the suicide
OL,19,Fof another person.
