OL,6,F"This case is a stark reminder of the
OL,7,Fdangers posed by those who aim to
OL,8,Fexploit vulnerable individuals online.
OL,9,FThe CPS will always aim to hold
OL,10,Foffenders to account when they
OL,11,Fillegally seek to encourage or assist
OL,12,Fa suicide.
OL,14,F"Our thoughts remain with the families
OL,15,Fof the victims, and we hope this
OL,16,Foutcome brings some measure of justice
OL,17,Fto them."
