OL,6,F"I hope today's admission provides the
OL,7,Fvictims and their families with some
OL,8,Fpeace of mind and relief that they are
OL,9,Fnow spared the ordeal of a trial. My
OL,10,Fthoughts, and those of the whole
OL,11,Finvestigation team, remain with them
OL,12,Ftoday.
OL,14,F"This has been a highly complex and
OL,15,Fsensitive investigation over the past
OL,16,F10 months, and I want to acknowledge
OL,17,Fthe courage of the witnesses who
OL,18,Fplayed an integral part in the
OL,19,Finvestigation during such difficult
OL,20,Fcircumstances.
